com.apriori.util

Class VariableDouble

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • com.apriori.util.VariableDouble
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public class VariableDouble
extends Number
implements Cloneable
    A simple variable reference for a double. This is the primitive specialization of Variable for double.

    This class is not thread-safe. This class is very similar to the boxed type Double except that it is mutable.
